OL,3,CCCTV shows moment stolen bus smashes
OL,4,Cinto barrier on six mile joyride
OL,6,FA #300,000 bus, stolen from
OL,7,FPortsmouth, has been left severely
OL,8,Fdamaged after being taken on a
OL,9,Fdangerous six mile joyride.
OL,11,FCCTV shows the vehicle being driven
OL,12,Ffrom the Lakeside Business Park to
OL,13,FWaterlooville, causing thousands of
OL,14,Fpounds worth of damage.
OL,16,FWithin minutes of it being stolen on
OL,17,Fthe evening of Bank Holiday Monday, it
OL,18,Fclipped a barrier, narrowly avoiding
OL,19,Fanother bus.
