OL,6,FSix miles away, the vehicle was then
OL,7,Fdumped.
OL,9,FThe person suspected of being behind
OL,10,Fthe wheel, can be seen casually
OL,11,Fwalking away, leaving its doors open
OL,12,Fand window smashed.
OL,14,FOwner and managing director of
OL,15,FXelabus, Gareth Blair, said most of
OL,16,Fthe profits made over the weekend will
OL,17,Fnow have to be spent on repairs.
OL,19,F"These buses aren't cheap. They're
OL,20,Fabout #300,000 each."
