OL,3,CCCTV shows moment stolen bus smashes
OL,4,Cinto barrier on six mile joyride
OL,6,F"We work hard as a small independent
OL,7,Fcompany to achieve vehicles of this
OL,8,Fstature and to see the state of the
OL,9,Fbus when it came back was
OL,10,Fheartbreaking."
OL,12,FThe bus had been in service over the
OL,13,Fweekend taking festival-goers to and
OL,14,Ffrom Victorious.
OL,16,FThe repair costs are estimated to be
OL,17,Faround #5,000.
OL,19,F"I would just like them to understand
OL,20,Fthe consequences of their actions."
