OL,4,Cinto barrier on six mile joyride
OL,6,F"At the end of the day, the bus can be
OL,7,Frepaired. However, he could have
OL,8,Fseriously harmed or killed someone. He
OL,9,Fshould take stock and account for what
OL,10,Fhe's done."
OL,12,FThe independent bus company, based in
OL,13,FEastleigh, said it's been devastated
OL,14,Fby the damage done, but it's now
OL,15,Fturning its attention to the repairs
OL,16,Fthat are needed.
OL,18,FIt wants to make sure the bus is back
OL,19,Fin service for when students return to
OL,20,Fschool next week.
